fields.name: WaveMaster Performance Surfboard
fields.description: The WaveMaster Performance Surfboard is designed for advanced surfers seeking high-performance and precision. It offers exceptional control and speed in all wave conditions.

fields.name: RidePro All-Round Surfboard
fields.description: The RidePro All-Round Surfboard is perfect for surfers of all skill levels. It's stable, easy to paddle, and provides a smooth ride on smaller waves.

fields.name: EpicWave Big Wave Surfboard
fields.description: The EpicWave Big Wave Surfboard is built for conquering the largest waves. Its performance and stability make it the choice of big wave riders worldwide.

fields.name: SunRider Retro Longboard
fields.description: The SunRider Retro Longboard brings back the classic style of longboarding. It's perfect for relaxed rides and nose riding in small to medium waves.

fields.name: AquaGlide Inflatable Surfboard
fields.description: The AquaGlide Inflatable Surfboard is a versatile and portable option for surfers on the go. It's easy to inflate and offers stability in various conditions.

fields.name: RipTide Performance Shortboard
fields.description: The RipTide Performance Shortboard is designed for aggressive maneuvers and quick turns. It's the choice of competitive surfers looking to push their limits.

fields.name: BeachBliss Mini Malibu
fields.description: The BeachBliss Mini Malibu is a beginner-friendly surfboard known for its stability and ease of use. It's a great choice for learners and casual surfers.

fields.name: LiquidRide Fish Surfboard
fields.description: The LiquidRide Fish Surfboard is a versatile option for small to medium waves. Its unique shape provides excellent speed and maneuverability.

fields.name: SwellTech Carver Surfboard
fields.description: The SwellTech Carver Surfboard mimics the feeling of surfing on land. It's designed for practicing maneuvers and improving your surfing skills.

fields.name: SeaRider Soft Top Surfboard
fields.description: The SeaRider Soft Top Surfboard is ideal for beginners and surf schools. It features a soft, forgiving top surface for safety and stability.

fields.name: WaveMaster Mini Simmons
fields.description: The WaveMaster Mini Simmons is a modern take on a classic design. It offers speed and maneuverability in a compact package for those seeking a unique ride.

fields.name: RidePro Performance Fish Surfboard
fields.description: The RidePro Performance Fish Surfboard is known for its versatility and wave-catching ability. It excels in a wide range of wave conditions.
